      "raw_text": "An examination of the eighth\ngrade pupils of the district schools\nof Spokane county will be held to-\nmorrow and Friday in the Masonic\ntemple, under the auspices OF\nCounty Superintendent Mcfarland.\nSeveral hundred pupils will take\nthe examination. 70 5yhs\n\n\nOn Thursday and Friday OF next\nweek there will be meeting Of the\ndistrict school teachers in the Ma.\nsonic temple. at which time Assist\nant State Superintendent Layhue\nwill explain the new school law.\n\n\nThe country schools of Spokane\ncounty will reopen either Septem'\nDer Z or Is."
